# Redirects and Rewrites for NyAnime
# Works with Netlify, Cloudflare Pages

# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS (handled by platform usually, but good to specify)
http://nyanime.qzz.io/*    https://www.nyanime.qzz.io/:splat    301!
http://www.nyanime.qzz.io/*    https://www.nyanime.qzz.io/:splat    301!

# Redirect non-www to www (canonical URL)
https://nyanime.qzz.io/*    https://www.nyanime.qzz.io/:splat    301!

# SPA fallback - all routes go to index.html for client-side routing
/*    /index.html    200

# API proxies (if using Netlify Functions)
# /aniwatch/*  /.netlify/functions/aniwatch/:splat  200
